---
title: Brie and Caramelized Onion Sandwiches with Fig, Apple and Arugula Salad
description: Fig jam and caramelized onions tangle together with ooey-gooey melted brie. The sweet richness is balanced by a bright and zesty apple, arugula and pepita salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwich-au-brie-et-aux-oignons-caramelises-9a68c10c.jpg
